scene.message:
Maki: Are you done with your{nl}
business? Let's hurry and{nl}
get out of here!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Wounds of the heart,{nl}
being invisible, are harder{nl}
to heal, it seems.{waitkey}{clearbox}No, no particular meaning.{nl}
It just crossed my mind{nl}
just now.{waitkey}{ret}

Mark: What are you lazing{nl}
around for? Once we're healed,{nl}
we move out!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: I want to vanquish the{nl}
Demons soon and restore the{nl}
peaceful town...{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: When's the day gonna{nl}
come that I'm the idol of the{nl}
whole town — no, all of{nl}
Japan~!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Ayase wants to go back{nl}
to being a normal high{nl}
school girl, and fast~!{waitkey}{ret}

Reiji: I'd like it if this{nl}
all got resolved soon.{waitkey}{clearbox}You've got someone waiting{nl}
for you to come home too,{nl}
haven't you?{waitkey}{ret}

Doctor: This place used to be{nl}
a peaceful, wonderful town{nl}
too, but it suddenly fell{nl}
to ruin.{waitkey}{clearbox}Now then, how are you{nl}
feeling?{waitkey}{ret}

Nurse: At this rate, this{nl}
town will perish. I can't{nl}
bring myself to feel any{nl}
hope either.{waitkey}{clearbox}I even catch myself thinking{nl}
it might be better if{nl}
everything just disappeared.{waitkey}{ret}
